public would be strongly condemned by the academy 
infantformula makers have traditionally refrained from 
advertising directly to the public and the academys longstanding 
policy has been to oppose such advertising narkewicz said 
the academys opposition stems from its concern that such 
product promotion may encourage women to use formula rather than to 
breastfeed their infants narkewicz said 
quite frankly narkewicz said if breastfeeding is the 
best and youve got a multimilliondollar promotion for formula 
whos going to put up the dough to advertise that breastfeeding is 
best nobody 
at a press conference in new york monday carnation announced 
