saturday with one count each of obstruction of justice and perjury 
after it was revealed the tapes he turned over to authorities were 
blank 
mcclease of jersey city nj claimed that sharpton had hired 
him to bug conversations involving the two brawley lawyers c 
vernon mason and alton maddox 
